caption:
Parenting teenagers can be hard. Your teen is dealing with developmental changes, emotional shifts, and hormonal influences while their friends and peers are going through the same things. 

They need support from parents or guardians at the same time that they’re gaining independence and trying to create their own identity.

Swipe through for positive parenting tips for teens.

Remember that if you’re in NYC, @nychealthy is providing teens (ages 13-17) free therapy via Talkspace. Learn more at the link in bio or talkspace.com/nyc
